'''哈曼国际工业公司'''（{{lang-en|'''Harman International Industries, Incorporated'''}}，简称：'''哈曼'''），是一家美國公司，其母公司為[[三星電子|三星電子]]，專为全世界的汽车制造商、消费者和企业设计和研发智联产品和解决方案，例如：[[智联汽车|智联汽车]]系统；音频和视觉产品、企业自动化解决方案；以及智联技术服务。<ref name=":0">{{cite web|title = HARMAN Unveils New Logo, Signals Brand Evolution|url = http://news.harman.com/releases/harman-unveils-new-logo-signals-brand-evolution|website = HARMAN Newsroom|access-date = 2016-01-11|archive-date = 2019-12-28|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191228121850/https://news.harman.com/releases/harman-unveils-new-logo-signals-brand-evolution|dead-url = yes}}</ref>总部设在[[斯坦福_(康涅狄格州)|斯坦福]]，哈曼主要业务在美洲、欧洲以及亚洲，其旗下拥有二十多个品牌 — 例如：[[爱科技|AKG]]、[[AMX_LLC|AMX]]、[[皇冠音響|Crown Audio]]、[[哈曼卡頓|Harman/Kardon]]、[[燕飛利仕|Infinity]]、[[JBL|JBL]]、[[JBL|JBL Professional]]、[[Lexicon_(company)|Lexicon]]、[[Mark_Levinson_Audio_Systems|Mark Levinson]]、[[瑪田音響|Martin]]、Revel、[[Soundcraft|Soundcraft]]和[[Studer|Studer]]。

==历史==
2016年11月14日，哈曼簽署了由韓國[[三星電子|三星電子]]公司收購的協議，<ref name="TechCrunch">{{Cite web|url=http://social.techcrunch.com/2016/11/13/samsung-harman/|title=Samsung is buying Harman for $8B to further its connected car push|last=Russell|first=Jon|website=[[TechCrunch|TechCrunch]]|access-date=2016-11-14}}</ref><ref name="CNN Money">{{cite news|last1=Mullen|first1=Jethro|title=Samsung buys auto electronics company Harman for $8 billion|url=http://money.cnn.com/2016/11/14/technology/samsung-harman-autos-connected/index.html|accessdate=14 November 2016|work=[[CNNMoney|CNNMoney]]|date=14 November 2016|archive-date=2017-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170810132029/http://money.cnn.com/2016/11/14/technology/samsung-harman-autos-connected/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>並於翌年3月10日完成收購。<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|url=https://news.samsung.com/global/samsung-electronics-completes-acquisition-of-harman|title=Samsung Electronics Completes Acquisition of HARMAN|website=news.samsung.com|language=en|access-date=2017-03-11|archive-date=2017-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170312064616/https://news.samsung.com/global/samsung-electronics-completes-acquisition-of-harman|dead-url=no}}</ref>

